title: Kenosha Bldg 2BR 1bath Condo across from St. Thomas
posting_body: ['Downtown  2 bedroom Condo across from  St. Thomas close to MCTC, UMN, MCAD .', 'New hardwood floors', 'Property Address', '1204 Harmon Pl.', '| 8 | Minneapolis, MN 55403', 'Offered By', 'MBJ Development Corporation |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'Check out this classic Manhattan style two bedroom condo.', 'The Kenosha Building is located across from St. Thomas University and allows for convenient downtown living  It is a corner unit with great light.', ' We will accept a cat for an additional $25.00 pet rent and a one time non refundable $200.00 pet fee.', 'Rents  includes all utilities except for lights.', ' There is FREE laundry & bike storage on site!', ' Perfect location for William Mitchel or MCTC students.', 'NOTE: YOU MUST CONTACT US TO APPLY - DO NOT FOLLOW LINK TO APPLY!', 'We require household income at least 2 1/2 times the rent.', ' We screen for rental history, criminal and credit.', ' In some cases we can accept a co-signer for 1st time renters.', '  Although parking is not included with the unit there is surface parking  for lease in the area.', 'Amenities', 'Hardwood floors', 'Wall air conditioner', 'exposed brick', 'remodeled kitchen high security entry', 'free laundry', 'Free bike storage', 'on-line rent payment', '24 hour emergency service', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 640', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,195.00', 'Application Fee: $75.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,195.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
